S = \left( \frac{ |n_A| r_A + |n_B| r_B + |n_X| r_X }{ |n_A| + |n_B| + |n_X| + \varepsilon } \right)

SizeMismatch = \frac{ | r_A - S | + | r_B - S | + | r_X - S | }{3}

ElectronegativityEffect = \frac{ | n_A | - | n_X | }{ r_A + r_X + \varepsilon }

Descriptor = \text{SizeMismatch} \times \left| \text{ElectronegativityEffect} \right|

where \varepsilon \text{ is a small constant to prevent division by zero (e.g., } 1\times10^{-6})
